INSERT INTO `comments` (`id`, `post_id`, `user_id`, `content`, `date_created`) VALUES
    (1, 11, 1, 'Great list of libraries! I had never heard of Vaadin before, but it looks like a great option for building web apps. Thanks for sharing!', '2023-02-11 21:43:57'),
    (2, 12, 6, 'I never really understood how garbage collection worked in Java, but your explanation made it much clearer. I\'ll definitely be more mindful of memory management in my future projects.', '2023-02-12 08:44:53'),
    (3, 15, 6, 'I wish I had read this post before I started my last project. I fell into the trap of hardcoding values, which made my code much harder to maintain. Thanks for the tips!', '2023-02-13 14:54:25'),
    (4, 14, 8, 'As someone who knows both languages, I think it really depends on what you want to do. If you\'re interested in data science or machine learning, Python is probably the way to go. But if you\'re building enterprise applications, Java is still the king.', '2023-02-13 16:11:21'),
    (5, 15, 7, 'This is exactly what I was looking for! I\'m working on a project that requires real-time chat, and I was struggling to get it working with Java. Your tutorial made it so much easier. Thanks a lot!', '2023-02-14 12:46:56'),
    (6, 13, 9, 'I\'ve used Apache Struts before, but I didn\'t realize it was no longer supported. Thanks for the heads up! I\'ll definitely be exploring other options for my next project.', '2023-02-16 12:47:16'),
    (7, 14, 8, 'I like that you covered both the strengths and weaknesses of each language. It\'s important to have a balanced perspective when making a decision like this. Thanks for the insights!', '2023-02-17 09:50:11'),
    (8, 15, 10, 'I\'m glad you mentioned the importance of testing. It\'s easy to forget about testing when you\'re caught up in the excitement of building something new. But it can save you a lot of headache in the long run!', '2023-02-17 12:49:04'),
    (9, 15, 9, 'I never really understood how to use WebSockets before, but your tutorial made it much clearer. I\'m excited to start experimenting with them in my own projects.', '2023-02-18 12:49:46'),
    (10, 12, 10, 'This is a great overview of Java memory management. I wish I had read something like this when I was first starting out with Java. Thanks for sharing your expertise!', '2023-02-19 12:52:06'),
    (12, 1, 13, 'Java is a versatile language used for creating a wide variety of applications. Its ability to run on multiple platforms and its rich set of libraries make it a popular choice for developers. Thanks for explaining its importance!', '2023-02-20 15:00:00'),
    (13, 8, 14, 'I completely agree with you. Despite the rise of newer languages and frameworks, Java remains one of the most widely-used languages in the world, and for good reason. Its versatility and reliability make it a great choice for many applications.', '2023-02-20 18:50:00'),
    (14, 2, 1, 'This is a great guide for anyone interested in becoming a Java developer. I especially appreciate the emphasis on continuously learning and expanding your skill set.', '2023-02-21 15:06:45'),
    (15, 2, 14, 'Thanks for sharing these resources! As a self-taught developer, I\'m always on the lookout for good learning materials. I\'ll definitely be checking these out.', '2023-02-21 18:06:00'),
    (16, 2, 14, 'Thanks for these tips! Writing efficient code is so important for making sure applications run smoothly and quickly. I\'ll definitely be keeping these principles in mind.', '2023-02-22 10:50:00'),
    (17, 4, 7, 'Debugging can be one of the most frustrating parts of programming, but these tips definitely make it easier. Thanks for sharing!', '2023-02-22 17:56:45'),
    (18, 1, 5, 'I\'m relatively new to Java and I found your post on sorting algorithms to be incredibly helpful. Your explanations were easy to follow and understand. Thanks for taking the time to share your expertise!', '2023-02-23 10:00:00'),
    (19, 7, 10, 'Your tutorial on multithreading in Java was really helpful. I\'ve struggled with this concept before, but your explanations and code snippets made it much easier to understand. Thanks for sharing your knowledge!', '2023-02-23 12:52:00'),
    (20, 6, 6, 'Your post on object-oriented programming in Java was a great read. I especially liked how you broke down the principles and provided clear examples. I learned a lot from your post!', '2023-02-23 17:10:12');
